{"id":149678,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/05/联合国难民署：已有约65万人逃离利比亚/","date":"2011-05-04T00:30:23Z","modified":"2011-05-04T00:30:23Z","title":"联合国难民署：已有约65万人逃离利比亚","content":"<div>\n<p> <span lang=\"ZH-CN\">的黎波里</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">在利比亚新一轮的激烈战事还未到来之前，从上周六开始，该国有约8000人逃往突尼斯南部。联合国难民署（</span><span>UNHCR</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）在日内瓦表示，难民中大部分是妇女和儿童。救援组织及世界粮食计划署打算向急需救济的利比亚民众提供食品和药物。此外，又有3200名利比亚难民抵达了意大利兰佩杜萨岛。难民中主要是萨哈拉南部国家在利比亚的务工者。据联合国难民署的数据显示，截至目前已有约65万人逃离利比亚，其中主要是外籍劳工。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&#038;ip=1&#038;img=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" border=\"0\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /><a href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&#038;ip=1&#038;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw-world.de%2Fdw%2Farticle%2F0%2C%2C15047144%2C00.html%3Fmaca%3Dchi-rss-chi-all-1127-rdf&#038;title=%E8%81%94%E5%90%88%E5%9B%BD%E9%9A%BE%E6%B0%91%E7%BD%B2%EF%BC%9A%E5%B7%B2%E6%9C%89%E7%BA%A665%E4%B8%87%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%83%E7%A6%BB%E5%88%A9%E6%AF%94%E4%BA%9A\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[15481,9037]}